{"tid":2254013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大米疑混塑膠粒　內地女子：吃飯聞到膠味","createTime":"2020-10-22T13:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T03:33:34.000Z","uid":209657,"like":235,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"a9cdb890f2311d828e578fa5ef810afe2a467cfc","tid":2254013,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201020/395227149449039872061845.jpeg/4v6beQKXL8rU2THfbKsVPbopTsWGegW-ptd7hKbXe4Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201020%2F395227149449039872061845.jpeg%2F4v6beQKXL8rU2THfbKsVPbopTsWGegW-ptd7hKbXe4Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0baf20aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我現在看到這些大米就反胃，之前已經吃了兩頓了！」，內地青島膠州市一名育有2子的媽媽日前大呻中伏，早前在市內李家河社區的商店購買了一袋10公斤重、產自黑龍江五常市長星米業的五常大米。她表示打開後吃了兩次，但每次吃飯都聞到一股塑膠味，起初還以為是電飯煲的問題，早前她洗米時卻見不少像塑膠粒的物體在水中飄浮，她才揭發事件。"},{"pid":"7dc978602f7e41a831d0533804ac2c9373ee6eae","tid":2254013,"uid":209657,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"來自青島膠州的劉女士是兩孩之母，她表示孩子們都愛吃飯，日前（16日）準備晚飯，洗米時卻見水面飄起一堆像塑膠的粒狀物體，在家作客的朋友與她細心研究，懷疑是塑膠粒製品。劉女士把大米放入電飯煲再加水，非大米的粒狀物體全都浮起來，她再嘗試用火測試，「我們用打火機分別對大米和那些像塑料的東西進行燃燒，發現大米經過加熱成焦糊狀，但那些顆粒卻像塑料一樣會燒成一團」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201020/395265431864610816395401.jpeg/o4NETolgvGoyGvmLbcwbvKzdqOvLi9XIVkNBRVZDQUU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201020%2F395265431864610816395401.jpeg%2Fo4NETolgvGoyGvmLbcwbvKzdqOvLi9XIVkNBRVZDQUU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f208a201&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec0910d78c84d0dc3a7f13ed5fac2a96f7ec0c75","tid":2254013,"uid":59522,"like":252,"dislike":3,"score":249,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"用膠咁重本？"},{"pid":"b90a381999e6a9cdaa4132dc5495a814aac47666","tid":2254013,"uid":21141,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"中國假米好多年歷史了<br />\n仲成日輸出外國<br />\n特別係益佢啲亞非拉兄弟"},{"pid":"05b2329d3bc5c4ad821bc125b26c630f09bc323e","tid":2254013,"uid":5523,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"b90a381999e6a9cdaa4132dc5495a814aac47666","tid":2254013,"uid":21141,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"中國假米好多年歷史了<br />\n仲成日輸出外國<br />\n特別係益佢啲亞非拉兄弟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"雜貨鋪賣唔怕比人找悔氣咩?"},{"pid":"7893bebf90f56395e743d57f8fd3c73dca12dac7","tid":2254013,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf82b13a626fe59f3113462d0543fef859a5fb1","tid":2254013,"uid":293677,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偉大祖国 成功解決糧食危機<br />\n膠粒可以養活十四億人"},{"pid":"d274eadb64d4cb90b603662d18b378c9fe004c0b","tid":2254013,"uid":26424,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"PP膠粒價錢係白米幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a5bf13d422369161660a43976c87d62f2345b5","tid":2254013,"uid":147916,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"終於有樣德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ed05dd1953dc3c95bdeae7f4ed3e568b2dc0f7","tid":2254013,"uid":364850,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"知唔知膠好貴架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲厭三厭四"},{"pid":"27e3cfc6dc60a808cd52c619c3b5ba8625b5cd9c","tid":2254013,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"劉女士於是拿着剩下的米向店家反映，但對方解釋他們只負責銷售，無法就大米的質量問題作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n該店家接受內地傳媒查詢時表示，他們多年來從一個姓譚的代理商進貨，每次5公斤裝的進20袋， 10公斤裝的也進20袋。而今次出問題的是長星米業的「五常大米」10公斤裝，店家稱從未遇過這情況；劉女士反映問題後，他們也即場拆開同一批次的大米，並未發現那種像塑膠粒的東西。<br />\n<br />\n內地記者曾致電代理商查詢，但接通電話後員工表示具體事情需要向老闆了解，之後沒有提供老闆的聯絡方式，亦再也不接聽記者的電話。內媒已就事件向膠州市市場監管部門反映，當局表示將盡快調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201020/395265422066192384078419.jpeg/Rwgmw88nRuyM8RuPj6CJoCPNrnHtE2_Yvohjkr6IY5I?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201020%2F395265422066192384078419.jpeg%2FRwgmw88nRuyM8RuPj6CJoCPNrnHtE2_Yvohjkr6IY5I%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9607d408&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33078f1a9e8304f72ca989f4f6e3ebce050f80c5","tid":2254013,"uid":25635,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"膠州食膠是咪特色黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8b2f29c4a48ead55add94ce7152cfde8f6605d","tid":2254013,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"塑膠師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171b14153a5f33015b062c1971ea17b7f8befd2c","tid":2254013,"uid":288152,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"內地女子：吃飯聞到鳩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4979e48e547a85308b0f1e6217f6373db0f243b9","tid":2254013,"uid":95519,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"quote":{"pid":"d274eadb64d4cb90b603662d18b378c9fe004c0b","tid":2254013,"uid":26424,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"PP膠粒價錢係白米幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"街邊執完膠切碎漂白應該唔貴掛<br />\n地溝油都差唔多<br />\n你要知道支共係環保方面行得好前"},{"pid":"d7f9d9d0bd7bdcf11dadca01e1a18c