eplyTime":"2020-10-22T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"大劣啲膠人係要食膠㗎。食地溝油佢話正苦幫佢哋強身健體練就百毒不侵嘅神軀，食毒奶粉佢話正苦幫佢哋Ｄ下一代增大頭腦個個有望做神童壽星公。我哋Ｄ正常人就唔好眼紅人哋，恭喜下佢哋咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839e5eeea9cf941bc92d0ad73c94c40be25efb51","tid":2254013,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4979e48e547a85308b0f1e6217f6373db0f243b9","tid":2254013,"uid":95519,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"quote":{"pid":"d274eadb64d4cb90b603662d18b378c9fe004c0b","tid":2254013,"uid":26424,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"PP膠粒價錢係白米幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"街邊執完膠切碎漂白應該唔貴掛<br />\n地溝油都差唔多<br />\n你要知道支共係環保方面行得好前"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ce24bb88c5bd192ed5ec467c7aee4e4bde6bcb","tid":2254013,"uid":69742,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d274eadb64d4cb90b603662d18b378c9fe004c0b","tid":2254013,"uid":26424,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"PP膠粒價錢係白米幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\nUpcycle 架麻"},{"pid":"23c76a8196a4bc5b1986087f604d32505d01c658","tid":2254013,"uid":28031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"用黎騙稱 但係膠唔係輕過米架咩<img src